summary: GAMBLE HOUSE UNITE! - In a world dominated by “the house always wins”, Gamble House ($DUCK) and his frens are looking to fight back! Inspired by people who have overcome all odds and beat the house! Gamble Duck and friends are looking to make a bunch of money, and retire in style. With unmatched dedication, the degen gamblers are back to show the house who is boss! The team has been assembled, the rockets are fueling up, it is time for the degens to take their wealth out of this world!
